;MONO-CRYSTALS OF LAMAE269S IN COMPLEX WITH MLG TRISACCHARIDES WERE OBTAINED AS FOLLOWED: 2 MICROL OF THE MIXTURE ENZYME/OLIGOSACCHARIDES (11,7 MG.ML-1 OF ENZYME, 0,04% (W/V) OF MLG DEGRADATION PRODUCTS) WERE ADDED TO 1 MICROL OF RESERVOIR SOLUTION CONTAINING 100 MM MIB BUFFER PH4.0, 17% OF PEG 1500 AND 10% OF GLYCEROL IN HANGING DROPS AT 12 CELSIUS DEGREE
